UNRELEASED (0.3):
    - You can now create handles to runtimes
    - Add monoio backend (enabled by default)
    - Added join handles
    - Spawn calls now handle shutdowns better
    - Blocking calls now return `Result<_, runtime::Error>`

0.2:
    - Move to a more object-oriented model with Runtime objects
    - block_on now runs in the current thread (will spawn a new runtime)
    - Support for block_on with return values

0.1:
    - Initial release
